Reasoning: The Lovasz Local Lemma is a well-known tool in discrete mathematics and theoretical computer science, and this paper presents a constructive proof of the general version of the lemma. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.CC (Computational Complexity), cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
